    • endGame

      public void endGame(String[] winnerNicknames) throws IOException
      this method displays a different page according to the result of the game for the actual player
      Parameters:
      winnerNicknames - (type list of String) nickname of winner players, if this parameter contains the nickname of actual player, winner page will be displayed otherwise the lose page will be displayed with the winner nicknames
      Throws:
      IOException - whenever there are problem with getting the fxml
